UID:foR1mdjTaZY82T7oNlw1N
SUMMARY:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - Lake Hills
DTSTAMP:20260320T020843Z
DTSTART:20260321T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Keep Bellevue Beautiful - Lake Hills\n\nEReed\n\nThu\, 02/05/20
	26 - 13:09\n\nMarch 21 2026\n\n9:00 AM - 11:00 AM\n\nAll Day Event\n\nOff\
	n\nEvent Registration\n\nOn\n\nContact\n\nEvan Reed\n\nEmail\n\nereed@bell
	evuewa.gov\n\nTelephone\n\n425-452-5372\n\nLocation\n\nSammamish High Scho
	ol\, 100 140th Ave SE\n\nDescription\n\nThe City of Bellevue's Keep Bellev
	ue Beautiful program is launching\n\n26 in '26\,\n\nan effort aimed at com
	pleting\n\n26 Signature Street cleanups\n\nin 2026. The goal is simple: sh
	ow up consistently\, take care of our streets and support cleaner\, more w
	elcoming neighborhoods.\n\nUpcoming Cleanup - Lake Hills\n\nDate:\n\nSatur
	day\, March 21\n\nTime:\n\n9-11 a.m.\n\nLocation:\n\nLake Hills neighborho
	od\n\nExperience is not required\, and cleanup supplies will be provided. 
	Come for the full two hours or drop in and stay as long as you can. Coffee
	 and water will also be available.\n\nTo register\, visit\n\nCleanLakeHill
