SUMMARY:North End Ecosocialism Reading Group
DTSTAMP:20260320T020843Z
DTSTART:20260326T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Armistice Coffee Roosevelt\\\, to discuss the book P
	ractical Radicals: Seven Strategies to Change the World\\\, by Deepak Bhar
	gava and Stephanie Luce\\\, through the end of Chapter 11. \\nYou don’t ha
	ve to live in the north end\\\, and you can feel free to join the conversa
	tion even if you haven’t had time to read.  Our biweekly discussions seek 
	to inform strategies for winning a democratic socialist society that thriv
	es ecologically. All are welcome! \\nWe sit outdoors in a breezeway–dress 
	warm. Any questions or difficulty getting the book\\\, please email greenn
	ewdeal@seattledsa.org.\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/north-end-ecosocial
	ism-reading-group-4/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
