	 in Seattle. \\nWe’ll be hanging out from 5:30pm–7:30 PM! Arrive before 6:
	00 PM to catch happy hour prices. The Beerhall also serves food\\\, includ
	ing $5.99 tacos on Tuesdays\\\, so you can grab a bite while you connect w
	ith folks from the working group. \\nAt 7:30\\\, trivia night starts—stick
	 around if you want to form a team with a few fellow DSA members and maybe
	 take home some bragging rights. \\nThere are several bus stops nearby\\\,
	 and there’s also a paid parking lot behind the bar if you’re driving. \\n
	Whether you’re already involved with the housing justice workgroup or just
	 curious and want to meet people\\\, all are welcome! Come say hi\\\, brin
